    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Rcov doesn&rsquo;t work after I upgrade rspec to 2.8,</p>

<p>here is a quick fix</p>

<p>add following code into your @spec_helper@</p>

<p><code>
require 'rspec/autorun'
</code></p>
